we are having an issue in the pdf loader qa, files are getting stuck when steps do not start in esp. The current job steps have completed but the next step does not start. 
Robert Johnson provided this information:
I saw that the job steps had been sitting in the ready state. 
There can be many causes, 
 
often see that the cause is something to do with the ESP agent and the ESP Manager not talking or slowly talking to each other for that job step(s) for some reason. Sometimes it is an issue with disk space writing to a log by the ESP agent and thread is locked and not talking to the ESP Manager anymore (see this when all job steps for single server get stuck in ready state), or network issue or sometimes ESP manager cannot write to logs. 
 
Sometimes job steps transition slowly in ready state. - A sluggish hand off or status between ESP Manager and Agent.  Not sure of all the causes.
 
In this case the job steps are from many different servers, so not an issue with a specific agent/server
